nvidia-graphics-drivers-367 (367.57-0ubuntu5) zesty; urgency=medium

  * Make the maintainer scripts behave better in chroots without kernels:
    - postinst: don't assume /boot/config-* exist, test -f before use.
    - postinst, postrm: test -x update-initramfs, don't short results.
    - preinst, prerm: test -x systemctl before use to skip ugly noise.
  * Move the uvm bits to amd64-specific patch to fix broken dkms on i386.

